Steps:
------
1. create restapi project with  below command in DOS prompt.
c:\>express restapi
c:\>cd restapi
c:\> npm install 

npm install body-parser@1.16 --save
npm install cors@2.8.4 --save
npm install ejs@2.5.5 --save
npm install method-override@2.3.7 --save
npm install  mongoose@4.8.3 --save
npm install node-restful@0.2.6 --save

completed server side module installation.
write routes , CRUD logic
-----------------------------------

client side application:

ng g component  product
ng g component product-add
ng g component product-detail
ng g component product-edit

add code for all components.

Add route configuration with in app.module and impor in 
ngModule.

Run the server : ng serve
----------------------
